    "human intervention occurred for quality checking.",
    "TableBank and DeepFigures contain used automatic procedures based on L A T E X and XML Moreover, considering what has been annotated in addition to how, we divide the datasets into three categories:• small-scale fully annotated, where the manual annotation is commonly used and document images come from scanners or digital cameras.",
    "• partially annotated documents, where the focus is mainly on finding and recognizing specific regions, such as tables or figures, two important objects for DLA.",
    "• large-scale fully annotated, collections-where automatic labeling is preferred because of the huge amount of data.These three main approaches for building datasets roughly follow also the timeline of research of the last 30 years.",
    "In the timeline shown in Fig. 4, the datasets are arranged in a chronological order and labeled according to the previous categories."
